column5: Looking for info on pickerel (walleye) fishing near Macleod Ontario such as Kenogamisis Lake. Thanks

Doug, if your asking about kenogamisis lake around geraldton don't waste your time. Fished it a couple of times and it was nothing to brag about. Lots of small fish. If you catch a 20 inch fish that would be a big one. I don't know if that lake is so heavily fished or not? Maybe look into fishing long lake never fished it before but might be worth looking into or h*ll just go to Lake nipigon and check out pasha lake cabins. Fisherman 1792
